{"tid":1944096,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"紙紮舖香燭滯銷 紙口罩應市","createTime":"2020-03-26T07:23:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-26T07:40:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"33fd5d3510075a1ae37dd123b3a4826bb97faf98","tid":1944096,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:23:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200326/J3VKMXIJXNVW3ZNWIPXFHBWI6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200326%2FJ3VKMXIJXNVW3ZNWIPXFHBWI6U%2F&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR3f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=680aa399\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200326%2FJ3VKMXIJXNVW3ZNWIPXFHBWI6U%2F&h=549296af\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200326/J3VKMXIJXNVW3ZNWIPXFHBWI6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n紙紮舖香燭滯銷 紙口罩應市<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】4月4日清明節正日，原是上山祭祖高峯期，惟港府因疫情加劇，籲公眾避免正日拜山增加傳播風險，建議公眾改用食環署十年前產物「無盡思念」，進行網上拜祭。有深水埗紙紮舖老行尊表示，今昔生意明顯有異，往年的同一星期，香燭最少回貨兩箱近千包，今年則賣剩貨，傳統祭品附薦袋造好五、六個，至今仍未賣完。不過老青兩代分別表示，上山地方更空曠，不太擔心感染，又指傳統就是傳統，並非「撳下電話」可以取代。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：女皇溫莎堡避疫 視像晤兒孫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200326/large/1585155208_6c3f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200326%2Flarge%2F1585155208_6c3f.gif&h=21cdb9f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n紙紮舖老闆歐陽秉志自製「紙口罩」祭品，限量發售。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n市民：網上悼念無意義<br />\n<br />\n本地拜祭還是回鄉祭祖，疫情下外出危機四伏，今年孝子賢孫都減少。寶華扎作老闆歐陽秉志在深水埗看檔廿年，承認與去年同一星期比較，人流不復現。「都冇計嘅，有疫情，邊個行業都死」。歐陽秉志指往年今日他已摩打手，不斷製作傳統附薦袋應市，但今年客人卻明顯減少，年初的香燭仍未賣完，附薦袋也不敢預先造太多，「要睇住銷情嚟做，因為掛滿都幾阻地方」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20200326/large/1585155208_6b6d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20200326%2Flarge%2F1585155208_6b6d.gif&h=c6bd90fd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n清明節將近，歐陽秉志（右）承認因疫情影響，客人減少。易仰民攝<br />\n<br />\n客少時間多，歐陽指閒時繼續做「藝術」，製作像真紙紮品，譬如「紙口罩」，不過製作需時限量發售，笑言只「貪得意」無人問津。時興在家工作，他說即使不在墳前燒祭品，寫了名在街燒衣也能送到先人手上，惟獨欠化寶設施。管理公、居屋的房屋署回應本報，今年清明節未有特別安排化寶鐵桶，提醒公眾違規化寶會遭扣分。私人物管公司太古地產亦表示，清明節期間，旗下物業不設置化寶設施。香港物業管理公司協會會長陳志球認為，增設化寶桶有違防疫原意，變相聚眾增風險，但明白公眾有需要，今日與業界開會商議處理方法。<br />\n<br />\n「無盡思念」是食環署十年前產物，旨在綠色殯葬，當局今年再呼籲大眾利用網上悼念。張小姐認為只是食環為做而做，「去唔到就係去唔到，如果你相信拜祭習俗，就會明白祭品的意義」。潘先生認為山上空間更廣闊，「有心唔怕遲」，會等人少再掃墓。<br />\n<br />\n■記者鄧溢禧"},{"pid":"951cb66fc13013bbed4d7c0914d1a938112e5794","tid":1944096,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:26:03.000Z","msg":"緊貼時事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53af10f429015f9338563ee0b78a470cc3918454","tid":1944096,"uid":321709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"951cb66fc13013bbed4d7c0914d1a938112e5794","tid":1944096,"uid":3454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:26:03.000Z","msg":"緊貼時事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:27:11.000Z","msg":"【立會要初選 「三不投」聯署】<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1943881\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1943881</a><br />\n聯署facebook專頁：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/legcopetition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flegcopetition&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR3f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=ed95c3a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/legcopetition</a><br />\n聯署Link：<br />\n<a href=\"https://forms.gle/LHAsuA6BQ58kC9RZA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforms.gle%2FLHAsuA6BQ58kC9RZA&d=NMuDHS38lj0XaiXuPCYWR3f7N2ZoUQ5IAXdO3fO0pAc%3D&h=69f1c96d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forms.gle/LHAsuA6BQ58kC9RZA</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/d1t7rTm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fd1t7rTm.png&h=d74c9cff&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"472f01302f551f801f5b2e51a531c09319d290fa","tid":1944096,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:35:03.000Z","msg":"先人都避唔到肺炎？"},{"pid":"9574d7614a9c8d2861ea90709e97836ca6cc5734","tid":1944096,"uid":49215,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-26T07:40:39.000Z","msg":"身前中肺炎死 死左又中多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}